   He stopped about 20 miles from the battle. He did not want to have prime 
know of his existence just yet. He sent a masquito bug out to the battle. It 
loooked just like a masquito but with much less noise. It watched as Prime 
began the attack. It would download his weapons and the skill it saw. It was 
about 500 feet from them at this point. Galvatron watched from his eyes 
sensors.
